Package uk.ac.open.kmi.iserve.sal.events

Class Summary
DocumentCreatedEvent DocumentCreatedEvent captures the creation of a document in the registry
DocumentDeletedEvent DocumentDeletedEvent captures the deletion of a document from the registry
DocumentEvent DocumentItemEvent captures all events related to a single document from the registry
DocumentManagerEvent DocumentManagerEvent is an abstract class capturing all events related to the documents manager
DocumentsClearedEvent DocumentsClearedEvent captures the event where the entire documents registry is deleted
Event Event is an abstract class capturing all the events that may occur in iServe
KnowledgeBaseClearedEvent KnowledgeBaseClearedEvent is the event triggered when the Knowledge Base is cleared
KnowledgeBaseManagerEvent KnowledgeBaseManagerEvent captures all the events related to the Knowledge Base Manager
OntologyCreatedEvent OntologyCreated captures the event where a new ontology has been uploaded to the knowledge base
OntologyDeletedEvent OntologyDeletedEvent captures the event where the an ontology has been deleted from the Knowledge Base
OntologyEvent KnowledgeBaseItemEvent captures events related to one single ontology
ServiceCreatedEvent ServiceCreatedEvent captures the creation of a service
ServiceDeletedEvent ServiceDeletedEvent captures the deletion of a service from the registry
ServiceEvent ServiceItemEvent captures events related to a single Service Item
ServiceManagerEvent ServiceManagerEvent is an abstract class for all Service Manager related events
ServicesClearedEvent ServicesClearedEvent captures the event whereby the entire services registry has been cleared.
